name: INSendPaymentPayeeUnsupportedReason
desc: Constants indicating the reason for being unable to resolve the payee.

items.name: case insufficientFunds
items.desc: The current user’s account has insufficient funds to make the payment.

items.name: case noAccount
items.desc: The payee does not have an account in your app.

items.name: case noValidHandle
items.desc: The unique handle that you use to identify the payee is invalid or missing.
